(956, 'What is Inventory Control Management ?', 'Inventory control, also called stock control, is the process of managing a company\'s inventory levels, whether that be in their own warehouse or spread over other locations. It comprises management of items from the time you have them in stock to their final destination (ideally to customers) or disposal (not ideal).', NULL, '2022-09-16 00:35:46');
